data.text: @TarunKolli_ Hi Tarun, if you have a Jetstar query we are here to gladly assist you. Just send us a DM to speak with an agent. Thanks - Bree
@turtlemagpies Hi David, That’s the kind of feedback we love to hear! You're welcome and we hope to see you again on board. Cheers - Norine

@levzekai I'm sorry that you feel this way. That doesn’t sound like the sort of experience we want any of our customers to have, @levzekai. Would you mind sending us a DM (Direct Message) so we can look into it further? Thanks - Ralph.
@merediiithann Hi Mezz. I am sorry to hear that you're having difficulties. Would you mind sending us a DM so we can assist? Thanks - Jay
@cappuccin0h We can check this out for you Melissa. Please send us a DM about this, please. -Lee
@kyleigh_wylie Hi there, we'd like to check this further. Can you send us a DM of your booking reference number and complete name, please? -Lee
@endeebee Hi, Nate can you send us a DM about this, thank you! -Lee

@BenHopkinsAus Hi Ben, sorry if you didn't receive a notification about your cancelled flight. We know how inconvenient cancelled flights can be and we try to avoid them as much as possible. We'd like to check this further for you. Please send us a DM with your booking reference. Thanks - Jaya
@ward1981honda Hi Ward, sorry if you need to wait that long in the line. We'd like to assist you with this. Please send us a DM so we can assist further. Thanks - Ryan
@e_watt93 Hi Elanor, I'm sorry to hear that. We’d love the chance to chat to you about this and assist. Could you please send us a DM with your booking reference and full name? Thanks - Leslie

@ourmaizcay We’re so glad that our LiveChat support team was on-hand to help make your experience with us a great one. We’ll definitely pass on the feedback to them (I’m sure it’ll make their day!) –  Jaya
@alblen Hi, sorry to hear you were unable to reach us. Please send us a direct message with your booking reference and full name so we can assist further. Thanks - Jaya
@WhincupCory Hi @WhincupCory. we’d love the chance to chat with you about this and see what we can do. Could you please DM us? Thanks – Ryan
@theadambrooksy Thanks Adam - we've responded now so please check your DM's 😊 - Jay
@theadambrooksy Hey Adam, that's not the kind of feedback we like to hear. If you require assistance with a booking, please DM us with your booking reference so we can assist. Thanks - Jay

@Sarab_Fearless Hey Sarab, sorry we missed your tweet - we're available 8am-8pm each day! I can see you've already got this sorted but feel free to DM us if you need further assistance. We'd also recommend you delete your original tweet as it contains your personal details. Thanks - Jay
@sjlangs You're welcome @sjlangs, feel free to send us a DM  if you need further assistance 😊. - Dan

@sjlangs Hi @sjlangs, You’ll always be eligible for a credit voucher for the full value of your booking if your Jetstar Airways flight is cancelled or affected by border restriction changes. Terms and Conditions apply. If you need further assistance please send us a DM. Thanks – Dan

@lisalovesbaconx Hi, You’ll always be eligible for a credit voucher for the full value of your booking if your Jetstar Airways flight is cancelled or affected by border restriction changes. Terms and Conditions apply. If you need to discuss a specific booking please send us a DM. -Dan
@sjpdavison Hi there, I appreciate how frustrating it is to be waiting for that long. Can you send us a DM of your booking reference and full name so we can assist you? Thanks - Bree

@formeraccount Hi Rhon, we’re offering passengers who are due to fly in or out of Sydney on or before 31st of July 2021 the option to cancel their trip and receive a credit voucher. If you require assistance with your booking, please send us a DM. Thanks - Leslie

@AlishaC50193590 Hi AlishaC, Sorry to hear your flight got cancelled and you've had a hard time reaching our Telephone Reservations Team. Would you mind sending us a DM here? We’d love the chance to chat with you about this and see what we can do. Thanks - Norine
@Andresfemon Hi Andre, would you mind sending us a DM with the details? We’d appreciate your feedback. Thanks – Jay

@shaunsmith76 Hi Shaun, we’re here to help! You’ll always be eligible for a credit voucher for the full value of your booking if your Jetstar Airways flight is cancelled or affected by border restriction changes. Terms and Conditions apply. Thanks – Jay

@Andresfemon We’re very sorry for the disruption you’ve experienced and for any inconvenience this meant for you and your family. The safety and well being of our customers is our highest priority and we will always ensure it’s safe to fly before we do so. Thanks - Dan
@dontdoitdani No worries, feel free to shoot us a DM for any assistance. Thanks - Norine
@blu_boys That’s the kind of feedback we love to hear - we’re sure Bree will love to hear it too. We’ll pass it on! – Jaya

@dontdoitdani Hi @dontdoitdani, I know this is not the outcome you are expecting and this must be upsetting for you. Would you mind sending us a DM here? We’d appreciate the chance to look into this further. Thanks - Norine

@bethdavis10 Sorry to hear about your previous experience. That’s definitely not the experience we’d want for customers like yourself, Beth. Thanks for letting us know so we can look into what happened here. You can still renew your membership to continue enjoy the exclusive offers. -Dan

@Andresfemon Hi Andres, I'm sorry to hear about your disrupted flight. We do our best to avoid delays – but sometimes things are out of our hands. If you want to discuss this further, please send us a DM. Hopefully, you’ll be on your way soon. – Jaya

@KariLyon_ Hi @KariLyon_, we know how inconvenient cancelled flights can be – and we try to avoid them as much as possible. Would you mind sending us a DM (direct Message) with more info? –  Thanks, Ralph.
@Timothy_Moran Hi Tim, we’d love the chance to look into this and see what we can do. Could you please DM us your booking details? Thanks – Jay
@MiB_Racing @MiB_Racing Hi, would you mind sending us a DM with your booking details? We’d appreciate the chance to look into this further. Thanks – Jay
@Aulify Hi Aulia, Sorry to hear you're unable to take your flight. Would you mind sending us a DM here? We’d appreciate the chance to look into this further. Thanks - Norine
@bohemothbibby Hi Rob, sorry to hear that you’re having trouble using our credit voucher. We'd like to look into this for you. Please send us a DM so we can assist further. Thanks - Jaya
@thatkittenlady Hi, @thatkittenlady. Sorry if you feel that way. We'd like to look into this for you. Please send us a Direct Message. Thanks - Dan

@l8on_p Hey @l8on_p, There’s nothing we like more than hearing that one of our passengers has had a great flight experience. Thanks for letting us know! Hope to see you soon on board, again! Thanks. - Ryan

@RiJac01 Hi @RiJac01, we know how inconvenient cancelled flights can be – and we try to avoid them as much as possible. Would you mind sending us a DM (Direct Message) with more info? We’ll see what we can do. –  Ralph.
@NathanMatchett1 Hi @NathanMatchett1. We’re usually very proud of the customer service our team deliver, so we’d like to look into this further. If you could DM us, we can get that started. – Jay
@SMTaylor_83 Hi Shannon. Flight schedules may change for a range of reasons. Rest assured however that options will be made available if there will be changes on your flights. Thanks - Ryan

@SMTaylor_83 Hi @SMTaylor_83, great that you are interested about flight from Melbourne to Busselton. You can check our flight available on our website at https://t.co/eMytl75Ru6 and for further update announcement about our launch from Melbourne to Busselton. - Thanks, Ralph.

@LuxuryOverdose Hi DJ, use of masks are mandatory on all flights and airports in Australia, except where a medical exemption exists. We've escalated this to management to follow up with our relevant teams to ensure team members are adhering to the correct requirements at all times. Thanks – Bree

@Saraalbalushi_ Hi @Saraalbalushi_, if you’ve already opted for a voucher, we’re unable to convert it to cash. Cash refunds are only available in specific circumstances. If you need to discuss a specific booking DM (Direct Message) us to speak with an agent. Thanks – Ralph.

@marlinman76 Hi thanks for your tweet. I understand your situation and we’d like to help you with your booking. Please contact us directly via DM with your booking reference and full name. Thanks - Chichi

@murrifullah That doesn’t sound like the sort of experience we want any of our customers to have, Wil. Would you mind sending us a PM so we can look into it further? Just key in the code JQINV585. Thanks - Ryan
@hubacekjirka Can you send us a DM of your booking reference number and complete name, please? We'd love to help you out! Thanks. -Lee
@kpfaulkner Hi Ken, we’d love the chance to chat to you about this and see what we can do. Could you please send us DM with the information about the email that you received? Thanks - Ryan
@BartMcCarthy3 Hi @BartMcCarthy3. We recognise your disappointment. We’d appreciate the chance to look into this further. Please us a DM for us to further help you with it. Thanks – Ryan
@hubacekjirka Hi Jirka, I'm sorry to hear that your flight has been cancelled. Feel free to send us a DM so we can discuss your options and assist. Thanks - Leslie

@MSL2035 Hi there, we know it’s upsetting to deal with uncertainty and we understand why you’d prefer a cash refund rather than a voucher. We'd like to check this further for you. Please send us a direct message with your booking reference and full name -so we can assist. Thanks - Jaya
@iMBananasaurus Hi Jordan, we know how inconvenient cancelled flights can be – and we try to avoid them as much as possible. If you need assistance on a specific booking, you may send us a DM. - Jay
@roomservice2259 Hi @roomservice2259, we know how inconvenient cancelled flights can be – and we try to avoid them as much as possible. Would you mind sending us a DM with more info? – Dan
@Rathdownepossum Hi, @Rathdownepossum. Thank you for reaching out. We'd like to look into this for you. Please send us a Direct Message. Thanks -Dan
@GeorgiosYdidi Hi Georgios, we know how inconvenient cancelled flights can be – and we try to avoid them as much as possible. Please DM if you need assistance on a specific booking. – Jay
@MBuschy Hi MBusch, sorry to hear that you're having trouble using the 'Manage My Booking.' We recommend clearing your cookies and cache, then trying again. Thanks – Leslie
@HenryBrodbeck Hi Henry, I am sorry to hear that. Would you mind sending us a DM with your booking details? We’d appreciate the chance to look into this further. Thanks – Jay
@Jacstreet Hi Jacqui, I am sorry to hear you're having difficulties. Would you mind sending us a PM quoting JQINV585? We’d appreciate the chance to look into this further. Thanks – Jay

@hubacekjirka @hubacekjirka Hi Jirka. I am sorry to hear that you're not happy with the outcome provided to you. I will be following this up and if you need further assistance, you may reply back to the email you received from your case manager. - Jay
@OliviaSPM Hi Olivia, I'm sorry to hear that you haven't received your refund yet. We'd like to check this further for you. Please send us a direct message with your booking reference. Thanks - Jaya

@Roxi_MW Hi Roxane, the use of masks is mandatory on all flights and in all airports across Australia, except where a medical exemption exists.  We ensure team members are adhering to the correct requirements at all times. Thanks – Dan
@emmacocoj @emmacocoj Hi Emma, would you mind sending us a DM with your booking details? We’d appreciate the chance to look into this further. Thanks – Jay
@NathanMatchett1 @NathanMatchett1 That’s definitely not the experience we’d want for customers like yourself. Thanks for letting us know so we can look into what happened here. Thanks - Jay
@nickwray Hi Nick, we’re sorry to hear you’re unable to travel as planned. Feel free to send us a DM so we can assist. Thanks – Ryan

data.text: @trofflollies We appreciate your concern about this Troff. Rest assured we'll pass this to the team to ensure and maintain social distancing. Thanks! -Lee
@philkef I appreciate your upset about this, Phil. I'll take note of your feedback. Thanks - Bree

@philkef Hi @philkef, I understand that this frustrating on your end, Carry-ons are weighed properly– so if your carry-on is over the weight limit, you’ll still have to pay an excess baggage fee. Thanks - Ryan
@x_Wanderer_ Hi @x_Wanderer_, we know how inconvenient cancelled flights can be – and we try to avoid them as much as possible. Would you mind sending us a DM with more info? Thanks – Ryan
@hugothestaffy Hi @hugothestaffy, I can tell you're disappointed. We’d like to look into this for you. So we can look into this further please send us a Direct Message (DM). - Thanks, Ralph.
@GeoffPolHist Hi Geoff, would you mind sending us a DM? We’d appreciate the chance to look into this further. Thanks – Jay

@Crazy_Old_Elise Thanks for reaching out Elise,  i'm sorry for the confusion. You can bring the CPAP machine as long as it can be put inside your main item. You can check details on our website at https://t.co/iOB9knxVC2. - Thanks, Ralph.

@Crazy_Old_Elise Hi Elise, you can bring assistive devices such as CPAP in addition to the carry-on baggage allowance as long as they are for personal use, do not exceed the maximum number of baggage items included in your fare and meet restrictions on carry-on baggage dimensions. Thanks - Norine
@tailsmoney Hi Kelly, I understand your situation. We’d like to help you with your booking, please contact us directly via DM with your booking reference and full name. Thanks - Chichi
@AusPetrolhead Hi @AusPetrolhead, we know how inconvenient cancelled flights can be – and we try to avoid them as much as possible. Would you mind sending us a DM with more info? Thanks. – Ryan

@tailsmoney Hi Kelly, I'm sorry to hear that you're unhappy with the outcome you received. You’ll always be eligible for a voucher if your flight is cancelled or affected by border restriction changes. T&C's apply. For further assistance, please send us a DM here. Thanks - Norine
@MsHungGEO Hi @MsHungGEO, we know how inconvenient cancelled flights can be – and we try to avoid them as much as possible. Would you mind sending us a DM with more info?Thanks. – <Ryan

@mcargy08 Hi Ron, I appreciate that you're having difficulties trying to cancel your flight. Can you send us a DM with your booking reference and full name? We'd like to look into this for you. Thanks - Bree
@MichaelBoer1 Thanks for getting back to us, Michael. We'd like to check this further for you. Please send us a direct message here with your booking reference and your full name. Thanks - Jaya

@MichaelBoer1 Hi Michael, I can see that the flight JQ - 940 Brisbane to Cairns at 9:45 PM is still scheduled to operate on the 7th of July. You can also check the status of any of your flights here: https://t.co/iEc5kam4ag Thanks - Jaya

@1monkeythinking Hi @1monkeythinking, I see how tough this situation is for you. We’d like to look into this for you. So we can look into this further please send us a Direct Message (DM). - Thanks, Ralph.

@vanetorrebolled Hi @vanetorrebolled, I understand that you would like to request a voucher for your flight. I can help you check your options. Please send us a Direct Message (DM) with your booking number and full name please. - Lee.

@WhoKnew53531000 Hi there, I'm sorry to hear that your flight has been cancelled. We know how inconvenient cancelled flights can be – and we try to avoid them as much as possible. Feel free to send us a DM so we can discuss your options and assist. Thanks - Leslie

@KateSharni Hi Kate, You’ll always be eligible for a credit voucher for the full value of your booking if your Jetstar Airways flight is cancelled or affected by border restriction changes. If you require assistance with your booking, feel free to send us a DM. Thanks – Leslie
@WiccanOfOz Hi, @WiccanOfOz. Thank you for reaching out. We'd like to look into this for you. Please send us a Direct Message. Thanks - Dan

@Ashley29991762 Hi Ashley, I understand that you prefer a cash refund. We're offering flexibility to bookings affected by restrictions to obtain a voucher. Refund can be available if your flight is cancelled depending on the circumstances. You can send a DM for further assistance. Thanks -Norine

@Ashley29991762 HI Ashley, If you’ve already opted for a voucher, we’re unable to convert it to cash. Cash refunds are only available in specific circumstances. If you need to discuss a specific booking DM(direct Message) us. Thanks – Ralph.

@GregPankhurst Hi Greg, I'm sorry to hear about your disrupted flight. We'd like to check this further for you. Please send us a direct message with your booking reference and full name. Thanks - Jaya

@GregPankhurst Hi Greg, you’ll always be eligible for a credit voucher for the full value of your booking if your Jetstar Airways flight is cancelled or affected by border restriction changes. Terms and Conditions apply. Thanks – Leslie
@JamieRoberts_Oz Hi, Jamie. Thank you for reaching out. We'd like to look into this for you. Please send us a Direct Message. Thanks - Dan
@willdace That’s definitely not the experience we’d want for customers like yourself, Will. Thanks for letting us know so we can look into what happened here. Thanks - Ryan

@AyalTusia Hi there, sorry to hear that you're unable to get through to our telephone reservations team. Would you mind sending us a DM with your booking reference and full name so we can look into it? Thanks - Leslie
@megankate6 Hello Megan. You may contact our Holiday's Team for further assistance regarding this matter. Just click this link to contact them: https://t.co/U9M3Mz282n. Thanks - Ryan
@Roxi_MW Hi Roxane, I'm sorry to hear about your experience. We’d like to help you with your booking, please contact us directly via DM with your booking reference and full name. Thanks - Chichi

@Chrisquirk Hi Chris, if you currently have a Holiday Package booked, our Jetstar Holidays is the best team to help you out. Just click this link to contact them: https://t.co/ckWaE0ahTd - and be assisted on your Holidays booking. Thanks - Bree
@Rachel_TazDevil Hi Rachel, would you mind sending us a DM with your booking details? We’d appreciate the chance to look into this further. Thanks – Jay
@jwelchnz Hello @jwelchnz. We are currently monitoring our network on a regular basis. You may check our website for further updates on the availability of our flights. Thanks - Ryan
@Pollyfronks Hi, @Pollyfronks. Sorry to hear that the flight was changed. We' like to look into this for you. Please send us a Direct Message and provide your booking details. Thanks - Dan

@SharpShard Hi, we consistently monitor our staff levels at peak periods and are training new staff to cut down waiting times. Unfortunately, although we aim to answer every call promptly, delays can still occur. Alternatively, you may send us a DM for further assistance. Thanks - Chichi
@ThompsonHolmes Hi Andy, I'm sorry for this inconvenience. We'd like to check this further for you. Please send us a direct message so we can assist you with this. Thanks - Jaya
@sweethaichilli Hi there, we'd like to assist you with this. Could you please send us a DM with your booking reference and full name? Thanks - Leslie

@judyanderson8 Thanks for reaching out Judy. Jetstar allow carriage of service dogs that are trained to assist people with disabilities. You can find out more here - https://t.co/7DInGLJn2Q. Thanks - Norine
